          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O to face the valley’s gloom without Him!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And without Him all eternity!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O the joy of having all in Jesus!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What a balm the broken heart to heal!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Ne’er a sin so great, but He’ll forgive it,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Nor a sorrow that He does not feel!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If I have but Jesus, only Jesus,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
